history.content:
Dear students;

The Center for Student Affairs will be closed beginning at noon on 12/23. We will reopen on January 3rd, 2017. During this time, most advisers will not be responding to emails or piazza posts. We look forward to helping you when we return from the break!

Have a restful holiday and a happy new year! 

- CSA
